msgid ""
"We would especially like to thank Dirk Eschler the &krusader; web master. If "
"you visit the <ulink url=\"https://www.krusader.org\">&krusader; website</"
"ulink> you will appreciate the hard work and effort that Dirk has put into "
"the site as much as we do."
msgstr ""
"Nos gustaría mostrar nuestro agradecimiento especialmente a Dirk Eschler, el "
"webmaster de &krusader;. Si visita el <ulink url=\"https://www.krusader.org"
"\">sitio web de &krusader;</ulink> podrá apreciar el duro trabajo y el "
"esfuerzo que ha realizado Dirk en él."

#. Tag: para
#: credits-and-license.docbook:105
